<div class='p-md'>
  <p class='m-b-md'>
    <h2 class='is-size-2'>Welcome!</h2>

    To get started, you'll need at least one friend.<br /><br />

    Then you'll be able to chat with them and create channels for communicating with groups of friends.

  </p>

  <div class='flex-row'>
    <a class='button m-r-md' {{action toggleModal 'show-my-info'}}>
      <span class='icon'>{{fa-icon 'share'}}</span>
      <span>Share My Info</span>
    </a>

    <a class='button' {{action toggleModal 'add-friend'}}>
      <span class='icon'>{{fa-icon 'plus'}}</span>
      <span>Add Friend</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
